30.poster.avif?t=1587970957\" width=620 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/bc2d9f9a090c1a5b5f8a6b85df0a0d30.webm?t=1587970957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/bc2d9f9a090c1a5b5f8a6b85df0a0d30.mp4?t=1587970957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enter one of the multiple online leagues available and develop your team in a season long competition against other coaches from all over the world. Be careful, death looms over the pitch and your superstar could end up with a broken neck before the end of the season… but hey, that’s what Blood Bowl is all about: scoring touchdowns, punching opponents in the face and dealing with deadly injuries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/4843a501feaa79f993b4ecd6cde16ba2.poster.avif?t=1587970957\" width=620 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/4843a501feaa79f993b4ecd6cde16ba2.webm?t=1587970957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/4843a501feaa79f993b4ecd6cde16ba2.mp4?t=1587970957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/c7dceca00ad135aad277d46756c9511d.webp?t=1587970957\" width=500 height=42 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602490/extras/ada681b0100e17aa1e9ad06d5ee3dcb8.avif?t=1587970957\" width=550 height=132 /></span><br><br><strong>Blood Bowl: Death Zone contains:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 14 teams 